"""kyth-exe-handler — intercept Windows .exe/.msi files and suggest Linux alternatives.

Registered as the default MIME handler for common Windows executable and
installer MIME types so that double-clicking a file in Dolphin shows a curated
suggestion dialog instead of silently failing or opening a hex editor.
"""

